description: STRING No. 70 // From 2021-05-01 // By Jonas Kasper Jensen www.jonaskasperjensen.com // Size 110 cm x 140 cm // The Trespasser is a series of AI-generated paintings created from an image set of the entire STRING collection from STRING No. 1 to STRING No. 65.
